[head=2]Procedure Context[/head][/color]

[bold]The individual was borged because:[/bold]
\[  ] They were deemed either legally or physically unrevivable, and either their will or the one with authority over the deceased selected borgification as the burial method.
\[  ] The individual committed a crime, and a court sentenced that individual to decorporealization.
\[  ] The individual is unprotected under space law, and a proper authority ordered for the individual to be borged. - Requires Captain or CC stamp.

